description: This is a market on whether a player who is not a Korean national wins the DreamHack Fall Starcraft 2 Masters tournament, to be held from September 7 to September 12.  If a player of Korean nationality wins the tournament, this market will resolve “No.”  Otherwise, this market will resolve “Yes.”  For the purposes of this market, only nationality is relevant, not where a player may currently reside.  The Korean players in this tournament are PartinG, Bunny, Dark, Trap, sOs, and Zoun.  All others are considered non-Korean. If the tournament is postponed to an end date on or before October 12, 2021, the same market conditions will apply. If the tournament is cancelled or postponed to an end date after October 12, 2021, the market will resolve 50/50.
